Class TestRunException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.itko.lisa.test.LisaException

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class TestRunException
extends LisaException
    This exception class contains the details of a run-time error in LISA. Errors coming back from the system under test should never cause a LISA exception! Only test case errors or bugs in the LISA code and components should cause Run Exceptions.

    See Also:
    (his companion on the load/init side), Serialized Form
